textfsm_template:
Value TIME (\d+\.\d+)
Value SOURCE_IP (\d{1,3}(\.\d{1,3}){3})
Value DESTINATION_IP (\d{1,3}(\.\d{1,3}){3})
Value STATUS (\w+)
Value TYPE (\w+)
Value QUERY (\S+)

Start
  ^\s*Time\s+Source IP\s+Destination IP\s+Status\s+Type\s+Query\s*$$
  ^\s*${TIME}\s+${SOURCE_IP}\s+${DESTINATION_IP}\s+${STATUS}\s+${TYPE}\s+${QUERY}\s*$$ -> Record
